I plead guilty to the charges brought against me and humbly request the court's compassion and understanding. I have no prior involvement in any criminal activities, and I sincerely believe that this unfortunate incident should not define my future. I am fully committed to making amends, both to the store and the community, and I am prepared to take any necessary steps towards rehabilitation.

Once again, I express my deepest apologies for my actions, and I appreciate the opportunity to address the court today. I am determined to grow from this experience and to prove myself as someone who can make positive contributions to society.

Thank you for your consideration.

Sincerely,
Melissa Cox
